OL,3,CReeves warned to avoid 'death by a
OL,4,Cthousand taxes' on businesses in Budget
OL,6,FThe chancellor has been warned not to
OL,7,Finflict "death by a thousand taxes" on
OL,8,FBritish business in the upcoming
OL,9,FBudget.
OL,11,FThe head of the Confederation of
OL,12,FBritish Industry (CBI) Rain Newton-
OL,13,FSmith said the government must "change
OL,14,Fcourse" and avoid heaping more costs
OL,15,Fon firms.
