OL,6,FRachel Reeves is expected to hike a
OL,7,Frange of will hike taxes to fill a
OL,8,Fblack hole in the public finances as
OL,9,Fshe faces the prospect of a downgrade
OL,10,Fin the Budget watchdog's economic
OL,11,Fgrowth forecast for every year of this
OL,12,FParliament.
OL,14,FAt the CBI's conference in
OL,15,FWestminster, Newton-Smith urged Reeves
OL,16,Fto stand up to Labour's backbenchers
OL,17,Fto take tough decisions on issues such
OL,18,Fas cutting welfare spending.
