OL,3,CReeves warned to avoid 'death by a
OL,4,Cthousand taxes' on businesses in Budget
OL,6,FShe encouraged Reeves to raise two
OL,7,Fbroad taxes, rather than increasing a
OL,8,Fseries of smaller ones.
OL,10,F"Prove it ` against opposition,
OL,11,Fagainst short-term politics, be it on
OL,12,Fwelfare, be it pension increases, show
OL,13,Fthe markets you mean business," she
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"Short-term politics leads to a long-
OL,17,Fterm decline, and this country cannot
OL,18,Fafford another decade of stagnation.
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@_O]xD@AOU
