OL,3,CReeves warned to avoid 'death by a
OL,4,Cthousand taxes' on businesses in Budget
OL,6,F"That means making hard choices for
OL,7,Fgrowth now before they get harder,
OL,8,Fhaving the courage to take two tough
OL,9,Fdecisions rather than 20 easier ones.
OL,11,F"Raising the headroom to make promises
OL,12,Fstick, it means one or two broad tax
OL,13,Frises, rather than death by a
OL,14,Fthousands taxes."
OL,16,FThe scale of the task facing the
OL,17,Fchancellor was underlined by a Sky
OL,18,FNews report that the Office for Budget
OL,19,FResponsibility has downgraded its
OL,20,Fforecast for 2026 and every other year
OL,21,Fbefore the next election due in 2029.
