OL,3,CReeves warned to avoid 'death by a
OL,4,Cthousand taxes' on businesses in Budget
OL,6,FReeves has already acknowledged
OL,7,Fpublicly that growth forecasts will be
OL,8,Fhit due to the OBR's revision of its
OL,9,Fassumptions about productivity.
OL,11,FThe downgrade, and the subsequent
OL,12,Freduction in tax revenues, will force
OL,13,FReeves to hike taxes to balance the
OL,14,Fbooks and build a bigger buffer
OL,15,Fagainst future shocks than the
OL,16,Fhistorically-low level of headroom she
OL,17,Fhas previously given herself.
