OL,3,CReeves warned to avoid 'death by a
OL,4,Cthousand taxes' on businesses in Budget
OL,6,FAt the CBI conference, Business
OL,7,FSecretary Peter Kyle promised measures
OL,8,Fto slash red tape for firms in the
OL,9,Fhope of boosting economic growth.
OL,11,FHe announced "a rolling programme of
OL,12,Findustry-led task forces to scrutinise
OL,13,Fregulation that's slowing down growth".
OL,15,F"These task forces will identify the
OL,16,Fred tape that needs to be culled and
OL,17,Fthey will recommend smarter, sharper
OL,18,Fregulation that builds and benefits a
OL,19,Fmodern, competitive business
OL,20,Flandscape," he said.
